                     <interp inst="t18220220-122-person1208" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Britton, a pawnbroker, at Battle-bridge. On the 9th of October, the prisoner pledged a table-cloth in the name of Dennett, Ashby-street.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220220-122-person1209">
